WEBVTT

00:00:00.830 --> 00:00:04.083
Hi,  my name is Fariel,

00:00:04.083 --> 00:00:06.127
but back home,

00:00:06.127 --> 00:00:08.463
I am also called the goat lady.

00:00:09.255 --> 00:00:15.344
And today I will be sharing the story
of how that came to be about.

00:00:17.221 --> 00:00:19.182
In 2015,

00:00:19.182 --> 00:00:24.353
I visited a small,
remote village in Pakistan

00:00:24.353 --> 00:00:25.813
called Pathan Goth.

00:00:26.272 --> 00:00:29.025
The residents of Pathan Goth

00:00:29.025 --> 00:00:33.946
were living without access
to basic facilities